name: Printing Panic
description:
It's finals season and you have just finished writing your final paper. It's not your best work, but it will do. 

Now you just need to pick it up at the library where the printer lies.

Will you be able to get there before you get caught by the guys in white? Or will you bump into a whole bunch of new people? Who knows, maybe you can even grab some free coffee. 

--

Keyboard Controls

Use the Arrow Keys to move around.

Press X/V to open your bag.

Press Z/C to cancel.

Press P/ENTER to open the Pause Menu.

--

Special Thanks to all those caffeinated drinks.
